==English==
===Etymology===
Variant of [[clew]] "a ball of thread or yarn," with reference to the one Theseus used as a guide out of the labyrinth.

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-uː|-uː]]

===Noun===
'''clue''' (plural: [[clues]])
# Any infomation that may lead one to a certain point or conclusion.
# A object or any kind of marking which may be used as evidence.

====Synonyms====
*[[hint]]

